flowchart LR
  Buttons[Buttons + Switches] --> UNO[Arduino UNO Q]
  Nicla[Nicla Vision: camera / audio / onboard IMU] --> UNO
  Sensors[RTC / Display / Haptics] --> UNO
  GNSS[Multi-constellation GNSS receiver + antenna] --> UNO
  Mag[Magnetometer] --> UNO
  Baro[Pressure sensor] --> UNO
  UNO --> Package[Observation Package]
  Package --> Photo[Photographic Witness records]
  Package --> Geo[Cartographic Witness records]
  Package --> Sync[Sync]
  Sync --> Web[Omoluabi Web Engine]
